==Swedish==

===Verb===
'''vicka'''
#[[wiggle]]; [[wobble]]; [[tilt]]
#:''Hon '''vickade''' på tårna.''
#:"She wiggled her toes."
#:''Om man '''vickar''' på det här locket tillräckligt länge går det av.''
#:"If you move this lid up and down long enough, it will break (off).''

====Etymology====
Since 1689 from the dialectal word ''vicka'' "yield; bend sideways; run in a waddling fashion". Most likely related to ''[[veck]]'' "[[fold]] (noun)" and ''[[vika]]'' "fold (verb)".